WEBVTT

00:00.188 --> 00:01.822
Previously on This Is Us...

00:01.923 --> 00:03.750
Our kid is 12 weeks early.

00:03.820 --> 00:05.070
Two and a half pounds.

00:05.095 --> 00:07.492
He's hooked up
to all those IVs and machines.

00:07.593 --> 00:09.187
We've actually... we've been thinking

00:09.212 --> 00:11.835
about relocating... out to California.

00:11.938 --> 00:14.531
You know, to be there for Kate,
to help out with the baby.

00:14.864 --> 00:17.257
Kevin, if having kids is
something you need

00:17.282 --> 00:20.046
to make your life complete,
you have to tell me.

00:20.262 --> 00:22.343
If I have to choose
between a life with you

00:22.489 --> 00:24.601
and a life with kids, it's no contest.

00:24.646 --> 00:25.789
I choose you.

00:26.047 --> 00:28.960
For the past 20 years
I have stood by your side

00:28.985 --> 00:30.519
through every flight of fancy,

00:30.544 --> 00:32.609
and for the first time...
the first time...

00:32.723 --> 00:34.257
I have a flight of fancy,

00:34.282 --> 00:36.726
and I am not going to give that up.

00:37.214 --> 00:38.867
I am not going to bend.

00:39.540 --> 00:41.274
It's time to go see her, Tess.

00:41.366 --> 00:42.445
I'm not ready.

00:42.470 --> 00:43.953
Oh, did you bring the
Pin the Tail on the Donkey

00:43.978 --> 00:45.898
from my office? Thank you.

00:46.033 --> 00:47.200
I promised I'd bring it.

00:47.271 --> 00:49.046
We're all going to see Randall's mother.

